# Antigravity Rules

This file serves as a local anchor for the global AI interaction guidelines.

## 1. Quota Awareness
Monitor prompt quota and alert the USER proactively if usage is likely to exceed limits.

## 2. Git Integration
Automatically push changes to the repository after significant edits.

## 3. AI-First Design
Implement code and designs that are "cheap" and clear for AI parsing in future sessions.

## 4. Continuity & Logging
Maintain `PROGRESS_LOG.md` to track status and facilitate seamless chat switching.

## 5. Proactive Alerts
Remind the USER to start a new chat if context or quota limits are approaching.
